Global Mercaptoacetic Acid Market Insights
Mercaptoacetic Acid Market size was valued at USD 0.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.25 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 6.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Mercaptoacetic Acid Market Overview
The global mercaptoacetic acid market has experienced significant growth in recent years, with the market size estimated at USD 100 million in 2023. This market is expected to grow at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.4% during the forecast period, reaching approximately USD 160 million by 2030. The increasing demand for mercaptoacetic acid across various industries such as pharmaceuticals, chemicals, and agriculture has been a key factor driving this growth. Its application in the production of metal corrosion inhibitors, agrochemicals, and in the synthesis of other chemicals is anticipated to fuel further expansion.

